SERVERALERT:
<html><body>
<h1 align="left">15th September 2021</h1>
<p>A new update has been deployed that: adds personal loot; fixes inspecting player talents; adds trinkets, capes, rings, and necklaces to the loot pools; adds a new treasure room to The Vault; improves The Timeway graphics; and fixes many minor bugs. Find out more in Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a><br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">20th August 2021</h1>
<p>The Timeways solo adventures are now available to play. The talent system has been replaced with a new XP based system.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">20th May 2021</h1>
<p>The new open-alpha is live and will run for about 2 weeks. Find out more in Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">21st February 2021</h1>
<p>A big update was recently pushed to the closed alpha test realm. Release notes are in <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">9th December 2020</h1>
<p>A lot of major updates have been pushed to the live realm for the weekend open alpha test. Please report any issues or feedback through our <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
